{% comment %}
  StyleHub Miami — About Us Page
  Design: DM Sans, Navy #1A1A2E, Red #E53E3E
{% endcomment %}

<div class="about-page page-width">

  <div class="about-hero">
    <h1>About StyleHub Miami</h1>
    <p class="about-lead">We bring you the best deals from top brands — all in one place, with a seamless shopping experience you can trust.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-content">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>StyleHub Miami was born from a simple idea: great products shouldn't come with a complicated shopping experience. We set out to build a modern online store that curates the best deals across fashion, beauty, electronics, home, and sports — making it easy for you to discover, compare, and buy with confidence.</p>
      <p>Based in Miami, FL, we combine the energy and style of our city with a commitment to quality, transparency, and customer satisfaction. Every product on our platform is sourced from trusted suppliers and top retailers, ensuring you get authentic items at competitive prices.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-values">
    <h2>What We Stand For</h2>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:#EBF5FB">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3182CE" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Trust & Authenticity</h3>
        <p>Every product is sourced from verified suppliers. No fakes, no knockoffs — just genuine products from brands you love.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:#E8F8F5">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#38A169" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Best Prices</h3>
        <p>We scan the market to find you deals that matter. Our curated selection focuses on value without compromising quality.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:#FEF5E7">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#D69E2E" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Customer First</h3>
        <p>Your satisfaction drives everything we do. From easy returns to responsive support, we're here for you every step of the way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="value-icon" style="background:#F5EEF8">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8E44AD" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 014 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 01-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 014-10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Wide Selection</h3>
        <p>From fashion and beauty to electronics and home goods, we bring you thousands of products across categories you care about.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-numbers">
    <div class="number-item">
      <div class="number-value">5+</div>
      <div class="number-label">Partner Retailers</div>
    </div>
    <div class="number-item">
      <div class="number-value">10K+</div>
      <div class="number-label">Products Available</div>
    </div>
    <div class="number-item">
      <div class="number-value">Miami, FL</div>
      <div class="number-label">Based In</div>
    </div>
    <div class="number-item">
      <div class="number-value">24/7</div>
      <div class="number-label">Online Shopping</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-cta">
    <h2>Start Shopping</h2>
    <p>Discover trending products, flash deals, and new arrivals — curated just for you.</p>
    <div class="about-cta-buttons">
      <a href="/" class="about-btn about-btn--primary">Explore Deals</a>
      <a href="/pages/help-center" class="about-btn about-btn--outline">Get Help</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
.about-page { padding:40px 0 60px; max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; font-family:'DM Sans',system-ui,sans-serif; }
.about-hero { text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px; }
.about-hero h1 { font-size:34px; font-weight:700; color:#1A1A2E; margin:0 0 12px; }
.about-lead { font-size:17px; color:#718096; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; line-height:1.7; }

.about-section { margin-bottom:48px; }
.about-content h2 { font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#1A1A2E; margin:0 0 16px; }
.about-content p { font-size:15px; color:#4A5568; line-height:1.8; margin:0 0 14px; }

.about-values { margin-bottom:48px; }
.about-values h2 { font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#1A1A2E; margin:0 0 24px; text-align:center; }
.values-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:20px; }
.value-card { background:#fff; border:1px solid #E2E8F0; border-radius:14px; padding:24px; }
.value-icon { width:52px; height:52px; border-radius:12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:14px; }
.value-card h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:#1A1A2E; margin:0 0 8px; }
.value-card p { font-size:13px; color:#718096; line-height:1.7; margin:0; }

.about-numbers { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:16px; margin-bottom:48px; }
.number-item { text-align:center; background:#F7FAFC; border-radius:14px; padding:28px 16px; }
.number-value { font-size:28px; font-weight:700; color:#E53E3E; margin-bottom:4px; }
.number-label { font-size:12px; color:#718096; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.04em; font-weight:600; }

.about-cta { text-align:center; background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1A1A2E,#2D2D4E); border-radius:20px; padding:48px 32px; color:#fff; }
.about-cta h2 { font-size:24px; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 8px; }
.about-cta p { font-size:15px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.7); margin:0 0 24px; }
.about-cta-buttons { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; }
.about-btn { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; padding:12px 28px; border-radius:10px; font-size:14px; font-weight:700; text-decoration:none; transition:all .15s; }
.about-btn--primary { background:#E53E3E; color:#fff; }
.about-btn--primary:hover { background:#C53030; }
.about-btn--outline { background:transparent; color:#fff; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); }
.about-btn--outline:hover { border-color:#fff; }

@media(max-width:768px) {
  .values-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  .about-numbers { grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); }
}
@media(max-width:480px) {
  .about-page { padding:24px 16px 40px; }
  .about-hero h1 { font-size:26px; }
  .about-cta-buttons { flex-direction:column; align-items:center; }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Us",
  "tag": "section",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "About Us" }]
}
{% endschema %}